  "explanation": "The defendant is a first-time offender who committed a non-violent financial crime involving $25,000. While the breach of fiduciary duty as an accountant is significant, the partial restitution demonstrates an attempt to mitigate harm. A sentence of 6 months serves as a punitive measure proportional to the theft while allowing for reintegration without the severe consequences of a long-term prison sentence.",
